race.description: Tab (N/P) Tg 1-4W Series 3 F Pr2 Division1
race.comment: HAYRIDE WARNER (8) was well in the market last time but only managed fifth (20.73), beaten 8 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in three starts. Should be very hard to beat this time. WATCH ME DESIGN (4) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (31.75) there two back. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from eight starts. Has ability and can atone. ZAIDEE DIVA (7) copped a check in the run and finished out of the placings when fourth (20.90) at this track over 342m in a TG1-4W. Can measure up this time. SMOOTH PARADISE (5) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
